%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^ORANGE%^Law Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

You follow a strict and ordered code of laws, and in so doing, achieve enlightenment.

Clerics with this domain gain %^ORANGE%^BOLD%^Touch of Law%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

This domain grants the ability to use the %^CYAN%^BOLD%^enhance%^RESET%^ command to place the axiomatic enhancement on your weapon.

This domain also grants +5 damage resistance against chaotic opponents.

The law domain contains the following spells:

Protection From Alignment, Align Weapon, Prayer, Deathward, Domination, Repulsion, Dictum, Shield of Law, Dominate Monster

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kreysneothosies, Lord Shadow, Seija

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
